extends ../layout

block content
  p
  ol.breadcrumb
    li.breadcrumb-item
      a(href='/') Home
    li.breadcrumb-item
      a(href='/companies') Companies
    li.breadcrumb-item.active= company.name

  .row
    .col-sm-2
      img(src='data:image/svg+xml;base64,').img-thumbnail
    .col-sm-7
      h3(style='margin-top: 0px')= company.name
      p Founded 1983 in Los Angeles.
      dl.dl-horizontal
        dt Company Name
        dd= company.name
        dt Legal Name
        dd= company.legalname
        dt FTC RN
        dd= company.RN
        dt Company Type
        dd= company.companytype
        dt Brands
        dd= company._brands
        dd= company._id
      p After a training at Parson’s School of Design, Beth Bowley launched her label in 1998. Before long, her designs were picked up by some of the top retailers: Henri Bendel, Barney’s and Fred Segal, among others. Her designs cater to the woman who is” young at heart and very witty and confident. She’s an intellectual babe who creates her own unique and inimitable style aesthetic.”
    .col-sm-3
      h4: strong Actions

  .row
    .col-sm-12
      h3 History
      table.table.table-condensed
        tr
          td October 15, 2009
          td Created by ImportBot
          td Initial record created, from the FTC RN Database